{"tid":1464903,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我求下你地，唔好成日諗住捉鬼啦。心裡有鬼，見乜都係鬼嫁啦。","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T16:21:18.000Z","uid":35211,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"79a6a253aae63505a886fa119750e8ecdff5a22d","tid":1464903,"uid":35211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心裡只有鬼，乜都做唔成嫁啦。之前一直唔散就係因為無顧住捉鬼啊。<br />\n<br />\n人一定比鬼多，只要大家獨立思考，d鬼就搞唔散我地嫁。唔好因為有手足比鬼搞，就草木皆鬼啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8072f9436e8af571e78afb57fad36d8612af10e1","tid":1464903,"uid":165840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:35:58.000Z","msg":"不分化不指責不割蓆"},{"pid":"2605f65cb85e3cb4d8b0be5c127c9d6b458d70f5","tid":1464903,"uid":90328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:36:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3132f72192e056d1cc002108f2a2d1325d6aaf16","tid":1464903,"uid":35211,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"不分化啊。唔好成日諗住身邊有鬼啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ca32ef026ab42b43569b301cbc94461523fca9","tid":1464903,"uid":164728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:37:27.000Z","msg":"獨立思考，唔好人地叫你做乜你就做乜"},{"pid":"f81b3ae191e3dc2e41949497d6ceb870e046cef3","tid":1464903,"uid":8724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTim